OL,4,CIncrease lobbying ban for ex-ministers,
OL,5,Curges watchdog
OL,6, Former ministers and top officials
OL,7, should face bans on lobbying government
OL,8, for up to five years, an ethics
OL,9, watchdog has said.
OL,11,FIn a report, the Committee on Standards
OL,12,Fin Public Life said the current
OL,13,Ftwo-year ban "may be too short in some
OL,14,Fcases".
OL,16,FIt also suggested rules on taking
OL,17,Fpost-government jobs should be written
OL,18,Finto civil servants' contracts.
OL,20,FThe recommendations come in the wake of
OL,21,Fthe Greensill Capital lobbying row.
